setAssetOutReceiver.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller does have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the asset out receiver is set to the zero address
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the asset out receiver is not set to the zero address
      ├─ when the asset out receiver is the same as the already configured one
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the asset out receiver is different than the already configured one
         ├─ it should set the asset out receiver
         └─ it should emit a AssetReceiverSet event
